  "detailed_description": "Hogvalord: The ranch is a relaxing and casual creature raising game. Immerse yourself in the joy of nurturing a variety of adorable Hogragons, explore landscapes with your newfound companions, and personalize your charming ranch with creative decorations. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/2204679ef2660306818b7e38dab7ad95.avif?t=1731290989\" width=606 height=110 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hatch and raise all type of Hogragons. Tending to their daily needs, watching them grow.<br></li><li>Evolve your Hogragons, each has their own features and special ability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Build houses and workplace to get extra income and products.<br></li><li>Decorate your ranch with various plants and stuffs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Enjoy a chill flight with the Hogragons as you search for exotic items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/7d021352b47621cf8a8c8da9b4a6bc33.avif?t=1731290989\" width=606 height=110 /></span><br>Hogvalord: The Ranch is a standalone title that takes place in the same universe of Hogvalord. A century after Lucas and his companions unveiled the secret of Hogragon, bringing these legendary beings back to the mortal realm, Hogragon has evolved into a coveted companion for all. Being a Hogmaster has become the dream profession for every child. Each year, newly graduated Hogmasters will be sent on a journey to remote regions. Their mission is to establish and nurture a ranch, help connecting these adorable creatures with new friends, allowing the locals to adopt their very own Hogragon.",
  "about_the_game": "Hogvalord: The ranch is a relaxing and casual creature raising game. Immerse yourself in the joy of nurturing a variety of adorable Hogragons, explore landscapes with your newfound companions, and personalize your charming ranch with creative decorations. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/2204679ef2660306818b7e38dab7ad95.avif?t=1731290989\" width=606 height=110 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hatch and raise all type of Hogragons. Tending to their daily needs, watching them grow.<br></li><li>Evolve your Hogragons, each has their own features and special ability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/db7a4a97a36cf05981d0fb7bf0a98246.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Build houses and workplace to get extra income and products.<br></li><li>Decorate your ranch with various plants and stuffs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/771d5888706fb85f32eeb7407f6fce49.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Enjoy a chill flight with the Hogragons as you search for exotic items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.poster.avif?t=1731290989\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.webm?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/9fe1aee7a8e717b94e812e28dcf9fe67.mp4?t=1731290989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829110/extras/7d021352b47621cf8a8c8da9b4a6bc33.avif?t=1731290989\" width=606 height=110 /></span><br>Hogvalord: The Ranch is a standalone title that takes place in the same universe of Hogvalord. A century after Lucas and his companions unveiled the secret of Hogragon, bringing these legendary beings back to the mortal realm, Hogragon has evolved into a coveted companion for all. Being a Hogmaster has become the dream profession for every child. Each year, newly graduated Hogmasters will be sent on a journey to remote regions. Their mission is to establish and nurture a ranch, help connecting these adorable creatures with new friends, allowing the locals to adopt their very own Hogragon.",
